casebody.data:
Kathleen LANE, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Andrew F. LANE, Jr., Defendant-Petitioner. C-901 September Term 2017
080720 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 1, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-1392/5553-14 and A-3474-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
